description:
Elder Marcus Mason talks about the unprecedented times we are living in and also another pillar of our faith The Sabbath. Once we realize the times, who is the last generation some important questions for us is how should we as Gods people be living in preparation to see Jesus in peace. What will Satan do to deceive people in the last days.

https://www.apocalypseministries.org/aptv/
